title: 103: Exeggutor
author: Chris Taylor
description:
Exeggutor is a walking jungle – the question is: WHERE ARE THEY COMING FROM? There is no jungle in Fake Japan – wait….they are the jungle!  

Hosts: [Chris](https://twitter.com/DaLiquidSword), [Mark](https://www.twitch.tv/robobobatron), [Aleksandar](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC56emXYp1pHXL2E9SLcYisw), [John](https://www.youtube.com/user/Haklex255)

For more episodes and the full ranking list visit [Magmar Sucks](http://www.magmarsucks.com) on the web.

For more on the Pokemon in this episode check out their [Bulbapedia page](http://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Exeggutor)
